data.description: This property presents an exceptional fixer-upper opportunity, being sold as-is and brimming with potential. Step inside this warm and inviting interior flooded with natural light, creating a welcoming ambiance throughout. The spacious living areas offer endless possibilities for customization and renovation to suit your unique vision. The oversized owner's suite is a true retreat, boasting a huge ensuite bathroom, providing ample space for relaxation and rejuvenation. Additionally, the finished basement adds versatility to the home, featuring a wet bar and the potential for a mother-in-law suite, offering flexibility for various living arrangements. Property also includes a 2-car oversized garage with high ceilings, perfect for storing vehicles and additional storage needs. Priced to sell quickly, this property presents an amazing investment opportunity with promising potential for a high return on investment. Whether you're looking to renovate and flip or create your dream home, this property is ripe with possibilities. Conveniently located just 3.7 miles from Wesleyan College and a short 17-minute drive from Tift College. Plus, with proximity to parks, shopping, dining, medical facilities, entertainment, and highways, everything you need is just minutes away.  Schedule a showing today and unlock the potential of this diamond in the rough. Disclosures are readily available from the seller.
